  "content_html": "<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:30px;\"><span class=\"color_25 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:30px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">VeroPoint בקר עם כרטיסי הרחבה</span></span></span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#787878;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFE;\">VeroPoint הוא בקר עצמאי ואוניברסלי הניתן לתכנות<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>\n( PLC/DDC ) שתוכנן במיוחד למטרות ניטור ובקרה<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>\nשל מערכות חימום ,אוורור, וקירור ( HVAC) ,בקרת מערכות<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>\nחשמל ואנרגיה ובקרת בחוג סגור.</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#787878;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFE;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#787878;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFE;\">VeroPoint הוא הפתרון האופטימלי לבקרה וניטור מערכות<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>\nבמבני ציבור, תעשייה, בתי חולים, מלונות.</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#787878;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFE;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#787878;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFE;\">VeroPoint הוא בקר עצמאי הכולל שעון מגובה סוללה<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>\nתוכנת הבקר מאוחסנת בזיכרון בלתי מחיק שאינו ניתן למחיקה.</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#787878;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFE;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#787878;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFE;\">בקר ה- VeroPoint  כולל מסך גרפי שניתן לתכנות כ – HMI<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>\nלתפעול מקומי נוח וידידותי למטרות תפעול לוחות זמנים וקבלת<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>\nנתונים בזמן אמת.</span></span></span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:40px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">מוצרים קשורים</span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\"> ישומי בקרה בע״מ</span></span></span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">יצירת קשר</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:left;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">טלפון: +972-3-6474998</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">​</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:left;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">פקס: +972-3-6474598</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:left;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">דואר אלקטרוני: <a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" data-auto-recognition=\"true\" href=\"mailto:cal@ddc.co.il\">cal@ddc.co.il</a></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">שעות פתיחה</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">ישומי בקרה בע״מ</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich